project). Modifications:

  - Host launcher functions (`void exl3_gemm(at::Tensor ...)` etc.) are left
    in place but no longer called — Rust drives launches via cudarc.
  - `<ATen/...>` and `<c10/...>` includes are replaced by the local
    `exl3_torch_stub.h`, which provides no-op replacements so vendored .cu
    files parse and compile to PTX without a libtorch dependency.
  - Training/quantization-only sources (`pack.cu`, `quantize.cu`,
    `coop_autotune.cu`, MoE-specific files) are removed.
  - `util.cuh` extended with explicit `#include <cuda_fp16.h>` and
    `<cuda_bf16.h>`; cuBLAS error helpers stripped (host-only).

